Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:18.65,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(130,130)}蝉时雨·精灵流
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.02,0:24:15.62,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 守电话·宣布紧急事态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:37.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:38.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的姐妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:42.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备前进 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:42.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方同伴在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.93,0:01:50.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边40° 准备发射主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:54.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离400
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:58.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装填手 装填弹种 定型炸药弹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:58.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:00.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:01.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:05.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关起来快三天了 在洗澡之前我是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:08.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:09.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:18.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击中目标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:21.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜 通知后续部队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:24.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我队击毁一辆 跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:25.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:27.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西娅 拜托掩护安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:28.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:33.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然闪闪发光的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:35.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过放心 那不是在打雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:46.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3…3点钟方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:13.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:19.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖纸吶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:44.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖竹签吶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 乃绘留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:24.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用点力压可洗不干净哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:48.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:55.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 虽然冬天冷 不过还好夏天凉爽啊 这栋建筑物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:59.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 今天不是梨旺前辈她们洗衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:02.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们好像很忙 叫我们替
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:03.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:05.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西娅姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:09.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太有食欲 叫我们吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:17.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么 你在准备晚饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:20.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:23.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿食物来玩会遭天谴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:25.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才不是在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为快到盂兰盆节了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？盂兰盆节是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fiesta des Lumieres
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}注：法语拼作Fête des Lumières，意为光之祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:33.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fi？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:38.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fiesta des Lumieres是赫尔维西亚南部特有的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:44.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基于夏天的一定期间内\N死者的亡魂会回到现世的民间信仰而举行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:49.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为把灵魂送回的记号 会把灯笼流到河中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:54.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某些地方也会把同样的节日叫做「盂兰盆节」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:55.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:57.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那么是一样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:05.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂会回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:08.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下等下 这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道幽灵会回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯笼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好像很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乡下也会烧烧火的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:18.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:22.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去的人会去天国 然后一直留在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:24.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人间徘徊的是坏东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:27.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在教会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:33.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 过来帮下忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:37.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们什么时候去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃 就买回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:43.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便还有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啊 祭司爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:56.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:06:58.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:06.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 做得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:10.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 教会也承认了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个Fi什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:16.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在中央主教区的话估计会有很大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这里是乡下地方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是随便
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:22.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乡下那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:27.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会用黄瓜和梨子做成马或者牛给祖先们坐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:33.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 为了安抚回来的祖先们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈们也会做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:42.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然去年光看着…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:59.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与地方居民进行良好的交流也是我们的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不纠结一些奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:03.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就只不过是个美丽的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 菲莉西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:21.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西娅姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:31.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:39.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长居然犯这样的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:41.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:46.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 最近连续几天都很炎热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:48.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没怎么睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西娅姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:02.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长有点奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:08.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时留下饭 一时又无视食费买西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:11.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也有自己的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:17.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也有不想告诉别人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她静一静吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:27.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘留？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我读了记录
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲身体验过那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:36.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:52.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西娅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:02.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好稳住 没错就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:05.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:13.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 出现了像队长一样的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:22.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片海洋在以前住着很多生物什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:24.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来你也不会相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:27.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:34.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「世界正逐渐接近末日 我们人类始终会完全灭亡」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:37.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个谣言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:42.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 如果那是真的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:46.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们到底是为了什么而在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:03.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊狄亚文字？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:51.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能读懂你最后的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:54.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的装备…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:58.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是旧时代的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:12.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织香少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:17.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:19.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:24.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…就只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:30.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…你在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:32.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:38.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还有人在这样的世界中活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:40.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:46.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们输了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:58.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输给那些家伙们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没能保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:26.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界终结了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:28.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是残渣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:36.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救幸存的人的泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:38.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:44.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界要重现昔日的繁荣已经是不可能的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别擅自决定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:48.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这就是真相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:52.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以尽管终结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种残渣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:15:01.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在绝望中悲哀地活着也太凄凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:04.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:09.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的世界活下去有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:11.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:35.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:45.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:46.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 请救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:11.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:20.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的部队能够早半天到达的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会变成这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊利亚皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:35.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我真有点吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么让你吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:41.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为梨旺去年完全无视Fiesta des Lumieres
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心境是怎样变化的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:51.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颜色很好看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:52.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是托雷兹产的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上次市场里面买回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:16:57.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美真美真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:08.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 那个人曾经是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:14.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想象那个人一样保卫国家 保卫人民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有时候我会想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:21.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个人真的回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:30.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让那个人告诉我答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 我被大家挂虑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:44.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没资格当队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:46.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是她们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:47.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:54.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 别一个人扛着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以听听你的倾诉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:17:59.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:02.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就恭敬不如从命地说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:03.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:05.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:10.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这夏天我胖了 正犯愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 冬服都快穿不进了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:19.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说单吃西瓜就能瘦下来 于是我就试一试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:26.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那个比嫩兰战线…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:35.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你不会认为我想起那个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:38.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:45.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小暮也做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:09.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我可没有相信亡魂什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:10.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是任务 任务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:12.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:15.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西娅姐要送谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:18.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧同僚和…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:21.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知名的某位士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我注意到重要的事情的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:28.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:30.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西娅姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么烦恼的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:37.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…可能帮不上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:38.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像让你操心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:49.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样太悲哀了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想操一操心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:56.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西娅姐一直操心我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你操心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:00.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想操一操心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:04.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我喜欢菲莉西娅姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:10.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜欢你 小彼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一直保持这个样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:15.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:18.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西娅姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:21.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都直言直语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:24.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕把自己的感情说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:29.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这是很了不起的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:40.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西娅 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:47.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:03.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请明年再来 祖先们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:25.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:28.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:33.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:38.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说这世界有什么意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:38.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:42.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我一个活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:44.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直在想过这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:48.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有我活下来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底有什么意义呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行不需要检查时间轴 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:51.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}听好了 不能在河边发呆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:53.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:58.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界 一定是没有什么意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:03.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这不是很美好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:09.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有的话 只要按自己的意思去寻找就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:15.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:18.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了我在这里的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:22.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}…然后啊 那时候竟然祭司爷爷亲手做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:23.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}然后呢 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:28.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}做得太难看了 最后还是靠由美奈姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:34.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会让她们遭遇我的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:36.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
